---
layout: base.njk
title: Forgotten Industries
description: An archive and evidence-based memoir that explores what happens to the things we leave behind; abandoned places, unfinished projects, deserted machines, and the parts of ourselves we once thought lost.
canonical: https://forgotten-industries.net/
---

<section class="masthead">
  <div class="section-inner masthead-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Archive & evidence-based memoir / established MMXIV</p>
      <h1 class="sr-only">{{ site.name }}</h1>
      <p class="tagline">{{ site.tagline }}</p>
    </div>
    <img class="hero-image" src="/assets/forgotten-industries.jpeg" alt="Forgotten Industries logo, EST MMXIV">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mirror-band" aria-labelledby="mirror-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Figure 1</p>
      <h2 id="mirror-heading">Seven routes. One archive map.</h2>
    </div>

    <div>
      <dl class="ledger">
        {% for item in site.nav %}
        <div>
          <dt>
            <span class="ledger-english">{{ item.english or item.label }}</span>
            {% if item.french %}
            <span class="ledger-french"><i>{{ item.french }}</i></span>
            {% endif %}
          </dt>
          <dd><a href="{{ item.href }}">{{ item.summary }}</a></dd>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </dl>

      <div class="stats" aria-label="Archive counts">
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>{{ archive.projects | count }}</strong>
          <span>Projects</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>{{ archive.inventory | count }}</strong>
          <span>Inventory records</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>{{ archive.fieldLogs | count }}</strong>
          <span>Field logs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>{{ archive.socialPosts | count }}</strong>
          <span>Social evidence</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="evidence-band" aria-labelledby="featured-lanes-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="mx-auto w-[min(760px,100%)] py-8">
      <p class="section-label">Public Spine</p>
      <h2 id="featured-lanes-heading">Entry 000 stays first.</h2>

      <p class="stamp-row mt-6" aria-label="Entry status">
        <span class="stamp">Manuscripts</span>
        <span class="stamp stamp-muted">Entry 000</span>
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">
        <a href="/posts/2026-06-06-prelude-a-thing-documented-is-a-thing-not-yet-lost.html">A Thing Documented Is a Thing Not Yet Lost</a>
      </h3>
      <p class="entry-note">Entry 000 / long-form origin manuscript</p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">
        <a href="/posts/2026-06-10-perspective-peregrines-and-pang.html">Perspective, Peregrines, &amp; “Pang”</a>
      </h3>
      <p class="entry-note">Entry 001 / first field doctrine</p>

      <p class="entry-note mt-4">
        <a href="/posts/index.html">View all curated posts</a>
      </p>

      <ul class="lane-list mt-8" aria-label="Public lane highlights">
        <li>
          <span>Manuals</span>
          <h3><a href="/hang-on-to-each-other/">Hang On To Each Other</a></h3>
          <p>Manual 001: recovered CaseLabs Mercury S8 assembly reference and living instruction shelf.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>Field Notes</span>
          <h3><a href="/field-notes/">Imported field signal</a></h3>
          <p>Short dispatches from the bench: evidence finds, measurements, restoration notes, and active process archived on-site.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>Projects</span>
          <h3><a href="/#projects">Dossiers and continuity</a></h3>
          <p>Long-running systems, object records, and project context packets that keep the archive coherent.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band" aria-labelledby="field-notes-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Field Notes</p>
      <h2 id="field-notes-heading">A continuity channel for the archive.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="callout">
      <h3>Subscribe</h3>
      <p>Short dispatches from the bench: restoration logs, evidence finds, measurements, recovered posts, and notes that do not need a full dossier yet.</p>
      <p class="action-row"><a href="/field-notes/">Open Field Notes</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band" aria-labelledby="shelves-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Shelves</p>
      <h2 id="shelves-heading">The site spine is an archive map.</h2>
    </div>

    <ul class="shelf-list">
      {% for shelf in site.shelves %}
      <li>
        <h3 id="{{ shelf.slug }}">{% if shelf.href %}<a href="{{ shelf.href }}">{{ shelf.label }}</a>{% else %}{{ shelf.label }}{% endif %}</h3>
        <p>{{ shelf.purpose }}</p>
        <p class="shelf-note">{{ shelf.tone }} {{ shelf.note }}</p>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

